OL,3,C'They just wanted to play and have
OL,4,Cfun', says family friend of Southport
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FA nine-year-old who died after being
OL,8,Fstabbed in Southport was just an
OL,9,F"innocent angel" just wanting to have
OL,10,Ffun, a family friend has said.
OL,12,FAlice Dasilva Aguiar died after a
OL,13,Fknifeman entered a Taylor Swift-themed
OL,14,Fdance class at the Hart Centre, on
OL,15,FHart Street, on Monday 29 July.
OL,17,FTwo other little girls, six-year-old
OL,18,FBebe King and seven-year-old Elsie Dot
OL,19,FStancombe also died after sustaining
OL,20,Fserious injuries during the
OL,21,F"ferocious" attack.
