OL,3,C'They just wanted to play and have
OL,4,Cfun', says family friend of Southport
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FAleck Jardim, a friend of Alice's
OL,8,Ffamily says there are "no words" to
OL,9,Fdescribe the loss.
OL,11,F"These were just little angels,
OL,12,Finnocent, they all just wanted to play
OL,13,Fand have fun," he said.
OL,15,FHe added: "I just can't imagine what
OL,16,FDavid and his wife are going through
OL,17,Fright now. I couldn't imagine myself
OL,18,Fgoing home and not seeing one of my
OL,19,Fdaughters.
