OL,3,C'They just wanted to play and have
OL,4,Cfun', says family friend of Southport
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,F"Nothing we can do that will bring
OL,8,Fthem back, but we just do our best as
OL,9,Fa community, that's all we can do
OL,10,Fright now."
OL,12,FEight other children suffered stab
OL,13,Fwounds and two adults were also
OL,14,Fcritically injured.
OL,16,FAleck said: "They tried to defend the
OL,17,Fkids as much as they could and they
OL,18,Fput their life on the line to protect
OL,19,Fthem, so they are real heroes for me
OL,20,Fand I'm very proud of the law
OL,21,Fenforcement."
