OL,7,FOn Thursday 1 August, Alder Hey
OL,8,FChildren's Hospital announced that two
OL,9,Fchildren who were injured in the mass
OL,10,Fstabbing had been discharged.
OL,12,FIn a statement Alder Hey Children's
OL,13,FNHS Foundation Trust said: "We are
OL,14,Fdelighted that two of the children
OL,15,Finvolved in Monday's awful incident
OL,16,Fhave now been discharged.
