OL,3,C'They just wanted to play and have
OL,4,Cfun', says family friend of Southport
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,F"We continue to treat five children
OL,8,Finvolved in the devastating incident
OL,9,Fin Southport on Monday, including one
OL,10,Frecently transferred to us from
OL,11,FAintree University Hospital.
OL,13,F"All the children in our care are
OL,14,Fcurrently in a stable condition. Out
OL,15,Fheartfelt sympathies remain with all
OL,16,Fthose affected by Monday's incident."
OL,18,FAxel Rudakubana, 17, was charged with
OL,19,Fthree counts of murder, 10 counts of
OL,20,Fattempted murder and possession of a
OL,21,Fbladed article on Thursday 1 August.
