OL,4,Cfun', says family friend of Southport
OL,5,Cvictim
OL,7,FHe continued: "The good thing is that
OL,8,Fthe local council, some companies,
OL,9,Fpolice and volunteers helped to clean
OL,10,Fup the mess and fixed what they could
OL,11,Fto help keep the mosque to look
OL,12,Fpristine as it was before and showed
OL,13,Fwhat Southport is all about.
OL,15,F"No matter what has happened Southport
OL,16,Fwill continue to be a resilient and
OL,17,Fpeaceful community".
